data.description: Great floorpan in a wonderful neighborhood in the West Forsyth HS district. Teen or in-law living available in the basement level. Main level large bedroom and full bath make guests feel cozy and welcome. Your Home is Your Castle, and we have the door to prove it !  Check out the authentic Castle Door and welcoming front porch. Outdoor living at it's best with a full upper level entertaining porch and stairs down to the recently hardscaped firepit and hammock area. Open concept living with 2 story light filled family room open to kitchen and breakfast area. The gas range brings out your inner chef. Available dining room is currently being used as a home office with plenty of natural light. Back door leads to the recently enlarged back porch with wooded view. Great for morning coffee and afternoon relaxing. The wide and open staircase leads to the family quarters featuring large bedrooms, custom closets, and roomy bathrooms. Owner suite features a large living area suitable for oversized furniture, seating area, and large owner suite bath, custom closet. The luxurious bath features a Spa tub and large shower with separate full sized vanities.    Downstairs is your partially finished basement with large bedroom and full bath, open concept living area, and 3 large vacant storage areas for holiday decor, outdoor cushions, gym, and all of your sporting equipment. See Virtual Staging photos for lower level living ideas. The garage includes built in enclosed shelving and a workshop area. Recently installed tankless water heater is a money saver for sure.    Home has been appraised, staged, regular maintenance visits, and quick close available for cash offers. Transferrable HSA Home Warranty is available for purchase. Move in ready. Washer, Dryer, and kitchen fridge remain. Custom cabinets in main and upper level closets and the kitchen pantry. Come see us this weekend !
